com.linkly.pos.sdk.service.impl

Class PosApiEventListenerProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.linkly.pos.sdk.service.impl.PosApiEventListenerProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPosApiEventListener

    public class PosApiEventListenerProxy
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPosApiEventListener
    Event listener proxy for IPosApiEventListener which will forward requests to a real event listener and provide error handling and logging.
